      "id": 361147,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>2-Butene-1-thiol is one component of skunk spray. How would you synthesize this substance (either cis or trans) from methyl 2-butenoate? From 1,3-butadiene?</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbmdYIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--538563c877c4e0f6e8655296a74bb75bc4c371d0/OChem_18_08_013.jpg\" alt=\"The structures of methyl 2-butenoate and 2-butene-1-thiol, separated from one another by two reaction arrows.\">",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": [],
      "collaborator_solutions": [
        {
          "images": [],
          "solution_type": "detailed",
          "content_html": "<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n<li><b>(a)</b> 1. LiAlH<sub>4</sub>; 2. PBr<sub>3</sub>; 3. <span data-math=\"{({\\rm H}_{2}{\\rm N})_{2}{\\rm C}\\text{═}{\\rm S}}\"></span>; 4. H<sub>2</sub>O, NaOH</li>\n<li><b>(b)</b> 1. HBr; 2. <span data-math=\"{({\\rm H}_{2}{\\rm N})_{2}{\\rm C}\\text{═}{\\rm S}}\"></span>; 3. H<sub>2</sub>O, NaOH</li>\n</ul>"
        }
      ],
